    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped to gradation 1 per the MRL 2 factor table and confirmed not-assessed per plan. Validation results demonstrate RH index agreement within 8.3% across all five CPB operating points, satisfying the RH < 1 acceptance criterion. A screening sensitivity exercise documented in the project technical memorandum confirmed low parametric sensitivity to viscosity and inlet boundary perturbations, supporting confidence in the nominal predictions. The overall credibility evidence is sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision for this Class II CPB device.",
